::Zardus::

Zardus nods, taking Kracken's pieces and putting them on a different 
table from Feline's. He'd wait till Squizzy was repaired, she was the 
bioengeneer after all.

Looking at the progress of the program that was running on FZ, he 
smiles, noticing that it was almost complete.
